description:
Online Meeting & Video Conferencing

Huawei Cloud Meeting offers secure and reliable videoconferencing with crystal-clear audio and ultra-HD video quality. Hold online meetings with staff or clients from a computer, mobile, or fixed room terminal.
1. Absent participants are also displayed in Participants;
2. Common participants can invite others to meetings;
3. You can perform remote support operations by shortcut keys;
4. You can check department details in Contacts;
5. Fixed known issues.
